      <section>
        <title>The quota formula</title>
        <chapter>
            <paragraph>
              Quota subscriptions are a central
              component of the IMF’s financial
              resources. Each member country
              of the IMF is assigned a quota,
              based broadly on its relative
              position in the world economy.
            </paragraph>
