      <section>
        <title>Key roles in the IMF</title>
          <chapter>
            <title>1. Subscriptions </title>
              <paragraph>
                It determines the maximum amount
                of financial resources the member
                is obliged to provide to the IMF.
              </paragraph>
            </chapter>
